wsSoleMibModule.name: wsSoleMibModule

revisions.description: Updated ranges for wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrPort and wsSoleAdapterCfgListenPort (1000..9000), wsSoleSiteDimension Length (0..3000), Width (0..3000), and Height (0..60), wsSoleTagTimestamp type changed to DateAndTime.
01a08 Added table for show rtls tags.
Added two more objects to wsSoleAdapterCfgTable. Added nodes wsSoleSwitchInfo, wsSoleSiteInfo, wsSoleMuLocateInfo and wsSoleSmartSurroundingsTable

wsSoleMibModule.description: MIB module for WiOS locationing services.

wsSoleAdapterSwTable.name: wsSoleAdapterSwTable
wsSoleAdapterSwTable.description: A table which shows all the information of existing SOLE adapter modules.

wsSoleAdapterSwVersion.name: wsSoleAdapterSwVersion
wsSoleAdapterSwVersion.description: The software version of the adapter.

wsSoleAdapterSwBuildDate.name: wsSoleAdapterSwBuildDate
wsSoleAdapterSwBuildDate.description: The date and time when the adapter was compiled.

wsSoleAdapterCfgTable.name: wsSoleAdapterCfgTable
wsSoleAdapterCfgTable.description: A table which is used to configure SOLE adapters.

wsSoleAdapterCfgLocateEnable.name: wsSoleAdapterCfgLocateEnable
wsSoleAdapterCfgLocateEnable.description: Enable or disable locationing of adapter type tags by on-board location engine.

wsSoleAdapterCfgLastErrorString.name: wsSoleAdapterCfgLastErrorString
wsSoleAdapterCfgLastErrorString.description: If any error happens during the enable/disable (config) operation, this scalar will show the most recent error message.

wsSoleAdapterCfgMulticast.name: wsSoleAdapterCfgMulticast
wsSoleAdapterCfgMulticast.description: Multicast MAC address to which aeroscout tags will send messages to.

wsSoleAdapterEngineTable.name: wsSoleAdapterEngineTable
wsSoleAdapterEngineTable.description: A table which shows all the existing external location engine connections.

wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrIp.name: wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrIp
wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrIp.description: The IP address of the location engine for adapter.

wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrPort.name: wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrPort
wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrPort.description: The port on which the external location engine is listening on.

wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrState.name: wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrState
wsSoleAdapterEngineAdptrState.description: The state of the location engine.

wsSoleAdapterEngineNumMsgsRxFromEngine.name: wsSoleAdapterEngineNumMsgsRxFromEngine
wsSoleAdapterEngineNumMsgsRxFromEngine.description: Number of messages received from engine.

wsSoleAdapterEngineNumMsgsTxToEngine.name: wsSoleAdapterEngineNumMsgsTxToEngine
wsSoleAdapterEngineNumMsgsTxToEngine.description: Number of messages sent to engine.

wsSoleAdapterEngineNumTagReportsTxToEngi.name: wsSoleAdapterEngineNumTagReportsTxToEngine
wsSoleAdapterEngineNumTagReportsTxToEngi.description: Number of tag reports sent to engine.

wsSoleAdapterEngineLastMsgRecvTime.name: wsSoleAdapterEngineLastMsgRecvTime
wsSoleAdapterEngineLastMsgRecvTime.description: Time at which last message was received by the engine.

wsSoleAdapterEngineLastMsgSentTime.name: wsSoleAdapterEngineLastMsgSentTime
wsSoleAdapterEngineLastMsgSentTime.description: Time at which last message was sent by the engine.

wsSoleSwitchSiteCoordinatesX.name: wsSoleSwitchSiteCoordinatesX
wsSoleSwitchSiteCoordinatesX.description: X coordinate for the switch's location. The unit is same as configured for site.

wsSoleSwitchSiteCoordinatesY.name: wsSoleSwitchSiteCoordinatesY
wsSoleSwitchSiteCoordinatesY.description: Y coordinate for the switch's location. The unit is same as configured for site.

wsSoleSwitchSiteCoordinatesZ.name: wsSoleSwitchSiteCoordinatesZ
wsSoleSwitchSiteCoordinatesZ.description: Z coordinate for the switch's location. The unit is same as configured for site.

wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesWholeLongitude.name: wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesWholeLongitude
wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesWholeLongitude.description: The whole portion of longitude of switch location (in deg). (example: if the longitude of switch location is -127.2345, this var should be set to -127)

wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesFractionLongit.name: wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesFractionLongitude
wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesFractionLongit.description: The decimal/fractional portion of longitude of switch location (in deg).(example: if the longitude of switch location is -127.2345, this var should be set to 2345).

wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesWholeLatitude.name: wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesWholeLatitude
wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesWholeLatitude.description: The whole portion of latitude of switch location (in deg). (example: if the latitude of switch location is -127.2345, this var should be set to -127).

wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesFractionLatitu.name: wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesFractionLatitude
wsSoleSwitchGeoCoordinatesFractionLatitu.description: The decimal/fractional portion of latitude of switch location (in deg). (example: if the latitude of switch location is -127.2345, this var should be set to 2345).

wsSoleSiteDimensionUnit.name: wsSoleSiteDimensionUnit
wsSoleSiteDimensionUnit.description: Unit of measurement for site (either feet or meters).

wsSoleSiteDimensionScale.name: wsSoleSiteDimensionScale
wsSoleSiteDimensionScale.description: Scale factor for site dimesions. Used for larger sites

wsSoleNumBarriers.name: wsSoleNumBarriers
wsSoleNumBarriers.description: Number of barriers configured within the site.

wsSoleNumDeployedAPs.name: wsSoleNumDeployedAPs
wsSoleNumDeployedAPs.description: Number of APs deployed within the site.

wsSoleSiteLastErrorString.name: wsSoleSiteLastErrorString
wsSoleSiteLastErrorString.description: If any error happens during any of site parameter config operation, this scalar will show the most recent error message.

wsSoleSiteBarrierType.name: wsSoleSiteBarrierType
wsSoleSiteBarrierType.description: Type of barrier (either of dry-wall, custom-wall, wooden door, metal door, concrete, metal shelf or custom shelf).

wsSoleSiteBarrierAttenuation.name: wsSoleSiteBarrierAttenuation
wsSoleSiteBarrierAttenuation.description: Attenuation in dBm caused by barrier.

wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesTable.name: wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesTable
wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesTable.description: A table where AP coordinates (x, y and z) can be configured.

wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesEntry.name: wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesEntry
wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesEntry.description: An entry in the wsSoleApCoordinatesTable, indexed by wsSoleApCoordinatesApMac.

wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesApMac.name: wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesApMac
wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesApMac.description: The MAC address of the AP, which is the index to this table.

wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesRowStatus.name: wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesRowStatus
wsSoleSiteApCoordinatesRowStatus.description: Row status: only values createAndGo (4) and destroy(6) can be set. A successfull created row shows row-status value as active(1).

wsSoleSiteApStatusTable.name: wsSoleSiteApStatusTable
wsSoleSiteApStatusTable.description: A table where AP coordinates (x, y and z) can be configured.

wsSoleSiteApStatusEntry.name: wsSoleSiteApStatusEntry
wsSoleSiteApStatusEntry.description: An entry in the wsSoleApCoordinatesTable, indexed by wsSoleApCoordinatesApMac.

wsSoleSiteApStatusApMac.name: wsSoleSiteApStatusApMac
wsSoleSiteApStatusApMac.description: The MAC address of the AP, which is the index to this table.

wsSoleSiteApStatusSwitchIp.name: wsSoleSiteApStatusSwitchIp
wsSoleSiteApStatusSwitchIp.description: Switch to which the AP is adopted.

wsSoleSiteApStatus11aRadioPower.name: wsSoleSiteApStatus11aRadioPower
wsSoleSiteApStatus11aRadioPower.description: Transmit power in dBm of 11a radio.

wsSoleSiteApStatus11bgRadioPower.name: wsSoleSiteApStatus11bgRadioPower
wsSoleSiteApStatus11bgRadioPower.description: Transmit power in dBm of 11bg radio.

wsSoleLocateMuAll.name: wsSoleLocateMuAll
wsSoleLocateMuAll.description: Boolean flag to enable Locating all MUs or stop locating all MUs.

wsSoleLocateMuInterval.name: wsSoleLocateMuInterval
wsSoleLocateMuInterval.description: MU Location Interval in secs. This decides how frequently the MUs are located (applicable to all located MUs).

wsSoleLocateMuMAC.name: wsSoleLocateMuMAC
wsSoleLocateMuMAC.description: MAC address of MU to be located.

wsSoleLocateMuRowStatus.name: wsSoleLocateMuRowStatus
wsSoleLocateMuRowStatus.description: row status for a row in wsSoleLocateMuTable.

wsSoleSmartSurroundingsType.name: wsSoleSmartSurroundingsType
wsSoleSmartSurroundingsType.description: Type of smart surroundings object: passive tag or fixed-mu.

wsSoleSmartSurroundingID.name: wsSoleSmartSurroundingID
wsSoleSmartSurroundingID.description: ID for smart surrounding object. Passive TAG ID or MU MAC.

wsSoleSmartSurroundingsLocX.name: wsSoleSmartSurroundingsLocX
wsSoleSmartSurroundingsLocX.description: X coordinate for smart surrounding object.

wsSoleSmartSurroundingsLocY.name: wsSoleSmartSurroundingsLocY
wsSoleSmartSurroundingsLocY.description: Y coordinate for smart surrounding object.

wsSoleSmartSurroundingsLocZ.name: wsSoleSmartSurroundingsLocZ
wsSoleSmartSurroundingsLocZ.description: Z coordinate for smart surrounding object.

wsSoleSmartSurroundingsRange.name: wsSoleSmartSurroundingsRange
wsSoleSmartSurroundingsRange.description: Read range for smart surrounding object. (Valid only for passive tags).

wsSoleSmartSurroundingsOrientation.name: wsSoleSmartSurroundingsOrientation
wsSoleSmartSurroundingsOrientation.description: Orientation (field of view) of smart surrounding object. (Valid only for passive tags).

wsSoleSmartSurroundingsRowStatus.name: wsSoleSmartSurroundingsRowStatus
wsSoleSmartSurroundingsRowStatus.description: Row status for a row in wsSoleSmartSurroundingsTable.

wsSoleTagLocX.name: wsSoleTagLocX
wsSoleTagLocX.description: Location X (real coordinates). Depends on wsSoleSiteDimensionUnit for the site.

wsSoleTagLocY.name: wsSoleTagLocY
wsSoleTagLocY.description: Location Y (real coordinates). Depends on wsSoleSiteDimensionUnit for the site.

wsSoleGroup.description: The group of current objects in wsSoleMibModule.
